data.description: Spacious home in quiet neighborhood. Just minutes from Beale AFB and HWY 70. This 2020 built home is perfect and in a great neighborhood off of Goldfields Pkwy. This 2 story home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms and 2475 Sq ft. The interior features vinyl plank flooring downstairs and recently cleaned carpet upstairs. Kitchen is spacious and open to the Livingroom and features stainless steel appliances including refrigerator and reverse osmosis water filtration system.1 bedroom and half bath downstairs perfect for guests.
